title: Uniform Interstate Family Support Act Forms
content:
Uniform Interstate Family Support Act Forms

State Regulations

Form UIFSA-1 - Child support enforcement transmittal #1-initial request

Form UIFSA-2 - Child support enforcement transmittal #2-subsequent actions

Form UIFSA-3 - Child support enforcement transmittal #3-request for assistance/discovery

Form UIFSA-4 - Uniform support petition

Form UIFSA-5 - General testimony

Form UIFSA-6 - Affidavit in support of establishment of paternity

Form UIFSA-7 - Locate data sheet

Form UIFSA-8 - Notice of determination of controlling order

Form UIFSA-9 - Registration statement

Form UIFSA-11 - Notice of registration of out-of-state support order

Form UIFSA-12 - Petition to vacate registration of out-of-state child support order

Form UIFSA-13 - Order on petition to vacate registration of out-of-state child support order

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
